            "title": "港股開市︱初段造好 恒指升267點報25606點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國減息預期大幅升溫，港股今早跟隨外圍揚升。恒生指數開市報25606點，升267點或1.06%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5731點，升84點或1.49%；國企指數以9176點開市，升97點或1.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股普遍造好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報120.4元，升2.03%；騰訊(00700)開報608.5元，升1.42%；美團(03690)開報119.1元，升0.59%；小米(01810)開報53元，升0.86%。滙控(00005)開報101.8元，升0.49%；友邦(01299)開報73.65元，升1.1%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250724_FI_source-web_09992-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250724_FI_source-web_09992-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指公司上周五收市後公布季檢結果，泡泡瑪特(09992)、中國電信(00728)、京東物流(02618)將納入恒指成分股，變動於9月8日生效。上述股份今早全線向上，泡泡瑪特再創新高，開墳30元，升3%；中電信開報6.33元，升2.73%；京東物流開報13.49元，漲3.85%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：東風集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508025_FI_source-web_00489.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：東風集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508025_FI_source-web_00489.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：東風集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東風集團(00489)擬分派從事新能源車業務的嵐圖股份並將之介紹上市，公司本身則會私有化；該股今早復牌應聲飆升，開報10.1元，漲69.18%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15202166-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87267%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125606%e9%bb%9e",
