            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報25666點，升314點，較上日現貨收市價25339點高水327點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5746點，升107點，高水98點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報9196點，升114點，高水116點。</p>\n</div>",
